<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="no-wonder">no wonder</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>难怪；不足为奇</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>With all these attractions, no wonder tourism is increasing wherever there is a Disneyland.
有这些引人入胜的东西，难怪哪里有迪斯尼乐园，哪里的旅游业就会发展起来。</p><footer>人教④ – 5</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Her child is missing. It is no wonder that she is so upset.
她的孩子不见了，难怪她如此心神不宁。</p></div></div>